    "attributes": {
        "action": "Implement mandatory anti-racism training for all police officers",
        "additional_details": "Since 2015, there has been a major spike in the rates of hate crime. Especially, around the time of the EU referendum and the BLM protests in 2020. Not to forget, the London Riots in 2011 which shook the nation.",
        "background": "We want the Government to require all police officers to undergo anti-racism training to help eliminate any racist bias within the police force.",
